<item>
            <title>[SOLR-17456] TransactionLog NPE</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-17456</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;In an erroneous case, a TransactionLog should throw an exception if an unexpected log file exists instead of merely log a warning in its constructor.  The latter leaves the file in a partially constructed state that leads to NPEs when it&apos;s used later.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
